            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De castiate et pudicitia atque impudicitia</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>¶ De castitate pudicitia atque impu
      <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>dicitia. ¶ Rubrica. 8.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>Ieophrastus.
      <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>in aureolo tractatu de nuptur. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e127">Illa
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>vere pudica est dicenda cui licuit
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>peccare: sed noluit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#V" n="52"/> ¶¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e139">Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiast. c. 26 For
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>nicatio mulieris in extollentia oculorum et
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>in palpebris illius agnoscetur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e152">¶ Terentius in heautontumerumeno. c. 10
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>Mulier compta faceta hec est meretrix. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e162">¶ Ouidius sine titulo seu amorum. l. i. c. 8.
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>Casta est quam nemo rogauit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>At si rusticitas non vetat ipsa rogat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e174">/ Libro. 3. et fi. c. 8.
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>Siqui metu dempto casta est: ea denique casta est
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>Que quia non liceat non facit: ipsa facit
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>Ut iam suans bene corpus: adultera mens est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e184">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e188">¶ Quintilianus declamationum. 2 decla.
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>Ego si qua est mihi fides pudicitiam in mi
        <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>lite etiam laudare erubeseo: feminarum est insta
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>virtus. Aliter mihi laudandus est vir fortis
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>idoneus bello: promptus ad pricula praestantis anim a </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e200">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e204">¶ Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum .vel. 11. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>i. Plures pudore peccandi quam bona volun
        <lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>tate prohibiti abstinent. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e212">
               <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e216">¶ Ualerius maximus. l. 2 ti. i. Massilia ci
        <lb ed="#V" n="73" break="no"/>uitas nullum aditum in scenam numis dat:
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>quorum argumenta maiori ex parte stupra
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>tionum continent actus talia spectandi comn
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>suetudo etiam imitandi licentiam sumat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e229">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e233">¶ Lex auten. ti. quomodo opem epos etc. §.
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>qui vero eas Pudicitia quam maxime mulieres
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>ornat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e241">
               <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e245">¶ Marcialis cocus epygrammaton vel 4.
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>Tanquam non liceat. nulla puella negat.
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>Casta igitur nulla: sunt caste null: equid ergo
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>Casta facit: non dat: non tamen illa negat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e255">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e259">¶ Maximianus: Castus amor veneris di
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>cite quando sitit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-d1e265">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90955-Qd1e269">¶ Montanarius in luna cleri. c. 3.
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>Res est difficilis casta bene ducere vitam.
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>Nulla fere maior quam casta viuere pena.
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>Sola namque suum finitur morte duellum. <!--270.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="116-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
